Package edu.vanier.selfdriving.controllers

Class GameController

java.lang.Object
edu.vanier.selfdriving.controllers.GameController
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameControllerAI
public class GameController extends Object
Class to control the game logic such as the timer, the camera, initialization of the game objects, etc. The Main controller of the Application.
